---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="頁面未找到 | 八字研究所"
  description="此頁面不存在，可能已被移除或網址有誤。"
  robots="noindex, nofollow"
>
  <section class="error-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="error-symbol">☯</div>
      <div class="error-code">404</div>
      <h1>此命格尚未被記載</h1>
      <p>你所尋找的頁面不在我們的命盤之中。或許是天機不可洩漏，也或許只是網址打錯了。</p>
      <div class="error-actions">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">回到首頁</a>
        <a href="/tools/chart-calculator" class="btn btn-outline">免費排盤</a>
      </div>
      <div class="error-bagua">
        <span>☰</span><span>☱</span><span>☲</span><span>☳</span>
        <span>☴</span><span>☵</span><span>☶</span><span>☷</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .error-page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-warm);
  }

  .error-symbol {
    font-size: 5rem;
    opacity: 0.15;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--crimson);
  }

  .error-code {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 15vw, 10rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--crimson);
    line-height: 1;
    opacity: 0.15;
    margin-bottom: -1rem;
  }

  .error-page h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .error-page > .container > p {
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .error-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .error-bagua {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    opacity: 0.1;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
</style>
